'''''The Godfather''''' d asaru amarikani n tejrimt, yeffeɣ-d deg 1972, yessufeɣ-it-id [[:en:Francis_Ford_Coppola|Francis Ford Coppola]] i yuran asinaryu akked [[:en:Mario_Puzo|Mario Puzo]], yebna ɣef wungal sɣur Puzo "The Godfather" i d-yeffɣen deg 1969. Asaru-agi ttekkan deg-s yisegbaren am [[:en:Marlon_Brando|Marlon Brando]], [[:en:Al_Pacino|Al Pacino]], [[:en:James_Caan|James Caan]], [[:en:Richard_Castellano|Richard Castellano]], [[:en:Robert_Duvall|Robert Duvall]], [[:en:Sterling_Hayden|Sterling Hayden]], [[:en:John_Marley|John Marley]], [[:en:Richard_Conte|Richard Conte]], akked [[:en:Diane_Keaton|Diane Keaton]]. Tidyanin n teqṣiḍt-agi ḍrant-d di twala seg 1945 ɣer 1955, taqṣiḍt-agi tḥekku ɣef twacult n Corleone i yḍefren [[:en:Vito_Corleone|Vito Corleone]] (Brando).
